<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <title></title>
    <link href="css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    
    <!-- Style Sandbox -->
    <style type="text/css">
        .maps-info
        {
            position:absolute;

            width:265px;
            height:145px;
            border:1px solid #333333;
            background-color:#333333;  
                      
            -webkit-border-radius: 5px;
            -moz-border-radius: 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
                       
            -webkit-box-shadow: #B3B3B3 3px 3px 3px;
            -moz-box-shadow: #B3B3B3 3px 3px 3px; 
            box-shadow: #B3B3B3 3px 3px 3px;
        } 
        .maps-info:after {
	        top: 100%;
	        left: 75px;
	        border: solid transparent;
	        content: " ";
	        height: 0;
	        width: 0;
	        position: absolute;
	        pointer-events: none;
	        border-color: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0);
	        border-top-color: #333333;
	        border-width: 20px;
	        margin-left: -20px;
        }
        
        .maps-info-flickr
        {

        }

        .maps-info-title
        {
            position:relative;
            height:20px;
            color:#ffffff;
        }

        .maps-info-title .glyphicon-menu-left
        {
            height:20px;
            width:20px;
            position:absolute;
            top:0px;
            left:0px;
            padding-top:2px;
            padding-left:1px;
            cursor:pointer;
        }

        .maps-info-title .glyphicon-menu-right
        {
            height:20px;
            width:20px;
            position:absolute;
            top:0px;
            left:244px;
            padding-top:2px;
            padding-right:3px;
            cursor:pointer;
        }

        .maps-info-flickr .maps-info-logo {
            background-image: url('images/Flickr.png');
            height:40px;
            width:52px;
            position:absolute;
            top:-10px;
            left:20px;
        }

        .maps-info-flickr .maps-info-title-text
        {
            position:absolute;
            top:0px;
            left:75px;
            width:150px;
            overflow:hidden;
            font-size:12px;
            padding-top:2px;
        }

        .maps-info-body
        {
            position:relative;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            height:110px;
        }

        .maps-info-body img
        {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 15px;
            max-width:80px;
            max-height:80px;
        }

        .maps-info-body .maps-info-attr
        {
            position:absolute;
            top:93px;
            left:4px;
            font-size:10px;
            width:130px;
            text-align:left;
            overflow:hidden;
        }
        .maps-info-body .maps-info-attr b
        {
            font-size:8px;
            font-weight:bolder;
        }
        .maps-info-desc
        {
            position:absolute;
            top:5px;
            left:110px;
            width:153px;
            height:88px;
            overflow:auto;
            overflow-x:hidden;
            overflow-y:scroll;
            font-size:12px;
            
        }

        .maps-info-footer
        {
            position:relative;
            padding-left:5px;
            color:#ffffff;
            font-size:10px;
        }

        .maps-info-buttons
        {
            position:absolute;
            top:-5px;
            left: 128px;
        }

        .maps-info-buttons>div
        {
            width:24px;
            height:24px;
            background-color:#333333;  
            font-size:14px;
            padding-top:1px;
            text-align:center;
            float:left;
            margin-left:6px;
            border:2px solid #333333;
                      
            -webkit-border-radius: 5px;
            -moz-border-radius: 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
                       
            -webkit-box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.7) 1px 1px 3px;
            -moz-box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.7) 1px 1px 3px;
            box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.7) 1px 1px 3px;
        }
        .maps-info-buttons>div:hover,
        .maps-info-buttons>div:active
        {
            background-color:#ffffff;
            color:#333333;
        }

        div.maps-info-close
        {
            margin-left:15px;
        }


        /*div.maps-info-close
        {
            background-color:#ffffff;
            color:#333333;
            padding-top:1px;
            margin-left:12px;
        }
        div.maps-info-close:hover,
        div.maps-info-close:active
        {
            background-color:#333333;
            border-color:#ffffff;
            color:#ffffff;
        }*/

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Sandbox</h1>


    <!-- Html Sandbox -->
    <div style="padding-left:50px;">


        <div id="infobox" class="maps-info maps-info-flickr">
            
            <div class="maps-info-title">
                <div class="glyphicon glyphicon-menu-left"></div>
                <div class="maps-info-title-text">Image Title</div>
                <div class="glyphicon glyphicon-menu-right text-right"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="maps-info-body">
                <img src="https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7624/16195987994_bbc4a49fab_q.jpg" />
                <div class="maps-info-attr"><b>BY: </b>Jason Daniel Pekovitch</div>
                <div class="maps-info-desc">
                    <p>Etiam efficitur nisl dolor, in bibendum justo ultrices vitae. Donec mattis iaculis urna. Aliquam nec mi tempus, facilisis est vitae, maximus ante. Maecenas in orci mi. Mauris id mattis dolor, id rhoncus lacus. Morbi mollis malesuada pellentesque. Nullam at quam.</p>
                    <p>Suspendisse potenti. Ut a enim id purus egestas eleifend eu quis enim. Sed augue ante, interdum sit amet lobortis eget.</p>
                    <p><b>TAGS:</b> #2011 #beauty #circletour #glaciernationalpark #goingtothesunroad #july #montana #redbustour #thegardenwall #travel</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="maps-info-footer">
                Aug 2, 2014 @ 4:17PM
                <div class="maps-info-buttons">
                    <div><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart"></span></div>
                    <div><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share"></span></div>
                    <div><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-resize-full"></span></div>
                    <div class="maps-info-close"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove"></span></div>
                </div>
                
            </div>
            <div class="maps-info-logo"></div>
            <div class="maps-info-arrow"></div>
        </div>

    </div>



    <!-- INCLUDES -->
    <script src="js/jquery-2.1.3.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js"></script>
    <script src="js/knockout-3.3.0.js"></script>
    <script src="js/NIC4Outdoors.js"></script>
    <script src="js/NIC4Outdoors.Maps.js"></script>

    <!-- Script Sandbox -->
    <script type="text/javascript">


    </script>


    </body>
    </html>
